Package scheduler

Interface CourseScheduler

All Known Implementing Classes:
ScheduleCourseSeq
public interface CourseScheduler
This interface is a CourseScheduler interface. It has a method to schedule and 2 other methods which will be used to return the personal directory and course directory after scheduling.
